    <title>Introduction</title>
    <para>
      Joala is an offspring of an internal development project started in 2011 at CoreMedia AG.
      The origin of Joala is the module conditions. <glossterm baseform="condition">Conditions</glossterm>
      implement a concept of busy waiting in your tests in order to execute the tests as fast as possible
      still being able to wait for a state of a given system.
    </para>
